'''邁克爾·布朗命案'''於2014年8月9日發生在[[美國|美國]][[密蘇里州|密蘇里州]][[聖路易斯縣_(密蘇里州)|聖路易斯縣]][[弗格森_(密蘇里州)|弗格森]]。事發時，18歲的[[非裔美國人|非裔美國]]青年邁克爾·布朗（{{lang-en|Michael Brown}}，以下簡稱布朗）在未攜帶武器的情況下，遭到28歲的白人警員達倫·威爾遜（Darren Wilson）射殺。<ref name="KeslingWSJ">{{cite news |first=Ben |last=Kesling |newspaper=[[The_Wall_Street_Journal|The Wall Street Journal]] |url=http://online.wsj.com/articles/missouri-teenager-killed-by-police-after-fight-1407698036 |title=Vigil for Missouri Teen Turns Violent |date=2014-08-11 |accessdate=2014-08-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141022104252/http://online.wsj.com/articles/missouri-teenager-killed-by-police-after-fight-1407698036 |archive-date=2014-10-22 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="ReferenceA">{{cite web |last=Lowery |first=Wesley |url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/even-before-teen-michael-browns-slaying-in-mo-racial-questions-have-hung-over-police/2014/08/13/78b3c5c6-2307-11e4-86ca-6f03cbd15c1a_story.html |title=Even before Michael Brown’s slaying in Ferguson, racial questions hung over police |publisher=The Washington Post |date=2014-08-13 |accessdate=2014-08-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140814105130/http://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/even-before-teen-michael-browns-slaying-in-mo-racial-questions-have-hung-over-police/2014/08/13/78b3c5c6-2307-11e4-86ca-6f03cbd15c1a_story.html |archive-date=2014-08-14 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url = http://www.pressdemocrat.com/home/2537611-181/ferguson-officer-in-fatal-shooting|title = Ferguson officer in fatal shooting identified, unarmed teen suspected of robbery (w/video)|last = Lieb|first = David|date = 2014-08-15|work = |accessdate = 2014-08-17|agency = Associated Press|last2 = Zagier|first2 = Alan|newspaper = The Press Democrat|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180809215601/https://www.pressdemocrat.com/home/2537611-181/ferguson-officer-in-fatal-shooting|archive-date = 2018-08-09|dead-url = no}}</ref> 布朗並未攜帶武器，<ref>{{Cite news|url = http://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/in-ferguson-three-minutes--and-two-lives-forever-changed/2014/08/16/f28f5bc0-2588-11e4-8593-da634b334390_story.html|title = In Ferguson, three minutes — and two lives forever changed|last = Roig-Franzia|first = Manuel|date = 2014-08-16|work = |accessdate = 2014-08-17|last2 = Brown|first2 = DeNeen|last3 = Lowery|first3 = Wesley|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140818011505/http://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/in-ferguson-three-minutes--and-two-lives-forever-changed/2014/08/16/f28f5bc0-2588-11e4-8593-da634b334390_story.html|archive-date = 2014-08-18|dead-url = no}}</ref> 且沒有任何犯罪記錄，在被射杀前他仅与警員接触了不到3分鐘。<ref name="Kirn">{{cite web |url=http://www.bizjournals.com/stlouis/news/2014/08/13/michael-brown-had-no-criminal-record.html |title=Michael Brown had no criminal record |work=St. Louis Business Journal |date=2014-08-13 |accessdate=2014-08-13 |author=Kirn, Jacob |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140814025548/http://www.bizjournals.com/stlouis/news/2014/08/13/michael-brown-had-no-criminal-record.html |archive-date=2014-08-14 |dead-url=no }}</ref> 當地警方認為布朗涉嫌一起搶劫案，但直到被射殺时他和警員之間都沒談到劫案一事。<ref name="latimes140815">{{cite news|url=http://documents.latimes.com/police-report-michael-brown-case/|title=Police report in the Michael Brown case|newspaper=Los Angeles Times|date=2014-08-15|access-date=2014-08-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140816005752/http://documents.latimes.com/police-report-michael-brown-case/|archive-date=2014-08-16|dead-url=yes}}</ref> 警員威爾遜已經在當地警局工作了4年，之前還有2年待在別的警局，<ref name=VegaWilliamsEckholm20140815>{{Cite news |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2014/08/16/us/darren-wilson-identified-as-officer-in-fatal-shooting-in-ferguson-missouri.html |title=Emotions Flare in Missouri Amid Police Statements |last1=Vega |first1=Tanzina |last2=Williams |first2=Timothy |last3=Eckholm |first3=Eric |date=2014-08-15 |work=The New York Times |accessdate=2014-08-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140815172428/http://www.nytimes.com/2014/08/16/us/darren-wilson-identified-as-officer-in-fatal-shooting-in-ferguson-missouri.html?_r=0 |archive-date=2014-08-15 |dead-url=no }}</ref> 也沒有違規記錄，<ref name="nymag140815">{{cite news|url=http://nymag.com/daily/intelligencer/2014/08/darren-wilson-shot-and-killed-michael-brown.html|title=Ferguson Police Officer Darren Wilson Shot and Killed Michael Brown After Alleged Robbery|date=2014-08-15|newspaper=New York Magazine|author=Joe Coscarelli|access-date=2014-08-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140817060133/http://nymag.com/daily/intelligencer/2014/08/darren-wilson-shot-and-killed-michael-brown.html|archive-date=2014-08-17|dead-url=no}}</ref> 還曾被稱讚敬業。<ref name="Officer Who Killed Ferguson Teen Given Award 6 Months Before Shooting">{{cite web | url=http://talkingpointsmemo.com/livewire/officer-brown-killing-awarded-commendation | title=Officer Who Killed Ferguson Teen Given Award 6 Months Before Shooting | publisher=TPM Tripwire | date=2014-08-16 | accessdate=2014-08-16 | author=James, Brendan | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140817045024/http://talkingpointsmemo.com/livewire/officer-brown-killing-awarded-commendation | archive-date=2014-08-17 | dead-url=no }}</ref>

這起事件引发連續多日的抗議行動，甚至出現暴動，警方派出大量警員、裝甲車，並發射了催淚瓦斯和橡皮子彈試圖平息騷亂，[[聯邦調查局|聯邦調查局]]（FBI）也介入調查<ref>{{cite news|title=美警濫殺青年爆騷亂 FBI介入調查|url=http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/international/art/20140813/18830300|accessdate=2014-08-15|newspaper=香港蘋果日報|date=2014-08-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140815233628/http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/international/art/20140813/18830300|archive-date=2014-08-15|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[美國總統|美國總統]][[巴拉克·奧巴馬|巴拉克·奧巴馬]]向布朗的家人發出慰問，並要求[[美國司法部|美國司法部]]進行調查。而在8月16日，為了維持當地治安，州長[[傑伊·尼克松|傑伊·尼克松]]宣佈當地進入[[緊急狀態|緊急狀態]]，这意味着弗格森午夜到上午五點間将實施[[宵禁|宵禁]]。<ref>{{cite web|title=Missouri governor imposes curfew in Ferguson, declares emergency|url=http://www.cnn.com/2014/08/16/us/missouri-teen-shooting/|publisher=CNN|accessdate=2014-08-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140824220529/http://www.cnn.com/2014/08/16/us/missouri-teen-shooting/|archive-date=2014-08-24|dead-url=no}}</ref> 然而，宵禁也無法控制局勢，因此第二天州長出動{{le|密蘇里國民警衛隊|Missouri National Guard}}以協助當地警察維持治安，宵禁命令則被撤銷<ref name=bbc-unrest>{{cite news|title=Ferguson unrest: White House steps up involvement|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-us-canada-28839522|accessdate=2014-08-18|publisher=BBC News|date=2014-08-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140819084130/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-us-canada-28839522|archive-date=2014-08-19|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=guardian-curfewfail>{{cite news|last1=Roberts|first1=Dan|last2=Swaine|first2=Jon|title=Obama sends attorney general to Ferguson as governor lifts curfew|url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/2014/aug/18/obama-attorney-general-eric-holder-ferguson|accessdate=2014-08-19|work=The Guardian|date=2014-08-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140819030107/http://www.theguardian.com/world/2014/aug/18/obama-attorney-general-eric-holder-ferguson|archive-date=2014-08-19|dead-url=no}}</ref>。虽然经历了大规模的抗议行动，涉案警官仍被判正当防卫，免于起诉。

==案情==

