in protest of police shooting, more than 30 arrests |newspaper=The St. Louis American |date=2014-08-11 |accessdate=2014-08-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181109222051/http://www.stlamerican.com/news/local_news/article_554e1212-2159-11e4-9dee-001a4bcf887a.html |archive-date=2018-11-09 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。警方运用防暴装备和直升机等装备，于凌晨2点驱散人群。两名警察在事件中受轻伤<ref name="Piper">{{cite news |last=Piper |first=Brandie |publisher=KSDK |location=St. Louis, MO |url=http://www.ksdk.com/story/news/local/2014/08/11/ferguson-riots-arrests-injuries/13886175/ |title=2 officers injured, 32 arrested during riots |date=2014-08-11 |accessdate=2014-08-11 |archive-url=https://wayback.archive-it.org/all/20140811180533/http://www.ksdk.com/story/news/local/2014/08/11/ferguson-riots-arrests-injuries/13886175/ |archive-date=2014-08-11 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

