c0.html#axzz3AMJHsXZ2|title = US police clash with protesters after black teenager's killing|last = Munshi|first = Neil|date = 2014-08-14|work = Financial Times of London|accessdate = 2014-08-14|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140815223452/http://www.ft.com/cms/s/0/50e27e8a-2374-11e4-be13-00144feabdc0.html#axzz3AMJHsXZ2|archive-date = 2014-08-15|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=I Am Mike Brown|url=http://www.argusradio.com/|website=Argus Radio|publisher=KARG Argus Radio|accessdate=2014-08-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140814150622/http://www.argusradio.com/|archive-date=2014-08-14|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

